#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn35.146"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn35.146:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 35 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 35 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.146:0.2"
msgid "15. Navapurāṇavagga "
msgstr "15. The Old and the New "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 146. Kammanirodhasutta → kammasuttaṃ (bj) | kammaṃ (pts1)
msgctxt "sn35.146:0.3"
msgid "146. Kammanirodhasutta "
msgstr "146. The Cessation of Action "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli4.133, sc1
msgctxt "sn35.146:1.1"
msgid "“Navapurāṇāni, bhikkhave, kammāni desessāmi kammanirodhaṃ kammanirodhagāminiñca paṭipadaṃ. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, I will teach you old action, new action, the cessation of action, and the practice that leads to the cessation of action. "

msgctxt "sn35.146:1.2"
msgid "Taṃ suṇātha, sādhukaṃ manasi karotha, bhāsissāmīti. "
msgstr "Listen and pay close attention, I will speak. … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.146:1.3"
msgid "Katamañca, bhikkhave, purāṇakammaṃ? "
msgstr "And what is old action? "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.146:1.4"
msgid "Cakkhu, bhikkhave, purāṇakammaṃ abhisaṅkhataṃ abhisañcetayitaṃ vedaniyaṃ daṭṭhabbaṃ … pe … "
msgstr "The eye is old action. It should be seen as produced by choices and intentions, as something to be felt. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.146:1.5"
msgid "jivhā purāṇakammā abhisaṅkhatā abhisañcetayitā vedaniyā daṭṭhabbā … pe … "
msgstr "The ear … nose … tongue … body … "

msgctxt "sn35.146:1.6"
msgid "mano purāṇakammo abhisaṅkhato abhisañcetayito vedaniyo daṭṭhabbo. "
msgstr "mind is old action. It should be seen as produced by choices and intentions, as something to be felt. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.146:1.7"
msgid "Idaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, purāṇakammaṃ. "
msgstr "This is called old action. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.146:1.8"
msgid "Katamañca, bhikkhave, navakammaṃ? "
msgstr "And what is new action? "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.146:1.9"
msgid "Yaṃ kho, bhikkhave, etarahi kammaṃ karoti kāyena vācāya manasā, "
msgstr "The deeds you currently perform by way of body, speech, and mind. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.146:1.10"
msgid "idaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, navakammaṃ. "
msgstr "This is called new action. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.146:1.11"
msgid "Katamo ca, bhikkhave, kammanirodho? "
msgstr "And what is the cessation of action? "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.146:1.12"
msgid "Yo kho, bhikkhave, kāyakammavacīkammamanokammassa nirodhā vimuttiṃ phusati, "
msgstr "When you experience freedom due to the cessation of deeds by body, speech, and mind. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.146:1.13"
msgid "ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, kammanirodho. "
msgstr "This is called the cessation of action. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.146:1.14"
msgid "Katamā ca, bhikkhave, kammanirodhagāminī paṭipadā? "
msgstr "And what’s the practice that leads to the cessation of action? "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.146:1.15"
msgid "Ayameva ariyo aṭṭhaṅgiko maggo, seyyathidaṃ—"
msgstr "It is simply this noble eightfold path, that is: "

msgctxt "sn35.146:1.16"
msgid "sammādiṭṭhi, sammāsaṅkappo, sammāvācā, sammākammanto, sammāājīvo, sammāvāyāmo, sammāsati, sammāsamādhi—"
msgstr "right view, right thought, right speech, right action, right livelihood, right effort, right mindfulness, and right immersion. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.146:1.17"
msgid "ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, kammanirodhagāminī paṭipadā. "
msgstr "This is called the practice that leads to the cessation of action. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.146:1.18"
msgid "Iti kho, bhikkhave, desitaṃ mayā purāṇakammaṃ, desitaṃ navakammaṃ, desito kammanirodho, desitā kammanirodhagāminī paṭipadā. "
msgstr "So, mendicants, I’ve taught you old action, new action, the cessation of action, and the practice that leads to the cessation of action. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.146:1.19"
msgid "Yaṃ kho, bhikkhave, satthārā karaṇīyaṃ sāvakānaṃ hitesinā anukampakena anukampaṃ upādāya, kataṃ vo taṃ mayā. "
msgstr "Out of compassion, I’ve done what a teacher should do who wants what’s best for their disciples. "

msgctxt "sn35.146:1.20"
msgid "Etāni, bhikkhave, rukkhamūlāni, etāni suññāgārāni. Jhāyatha, bhikkhave, mā pamādattha; mā pacchāvippaṭisārino ahuvattha. Ayaṃ vo amhākaṃ anusāsanī”ti. "
msgstr "Here are these roots of trees, and here are these empty huts. Practice absorption, mendicants! Don’t be negligent! Don’t regret it later! This is my instruction to you.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn35.146:1.21"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

